<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,309,486]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,431,309,338]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">Material examined –</emphasis>
This species was collected as vagrant on leaves of apple trees, 
<taxonomicName authority="Borkh." authorityName="Borkh." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Malus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="domestica">
<emphasis box="[1220,1436,310,339]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">Malus domestica</emphasis>
Borkh.
</taxonomicName>
(
<taxonomicName box="[256,385,347,376]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Rosaceae</taxonomicName>
). The activity of this species in high densities leads to light rust or browning of the leaves. Twenty-eight (28) females and 
<materialsCitation box="[655,1385,383,413]" collectingDate="2017-08-11" collectorName="Khorramabad" location="Chaghalvandi" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" specimenCount="13" specimenCount-male="13">
<specimenCount box="[655,774,383,412]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" type="male">13 males</specimenCount>
, 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:45565D62FFA0B323FDFBFF5FFE74F7FB:C820BAAFFFA0B323FCDFFECCFC0DF4F9" box="[788,969,383,412]" name="Chaghalvandi" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">Chaghalvandi</location>
, 
<collectorName box="[982,1161,383,412]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115">Khorramabad</collectorName>
, 
<date box="[1175,1385,383,413]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" value="2017-08-11">
<collectingDate box="[1175,1385,383,413]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" value="2017-08-11">11 August 2017</collectingDate>
</date>
</materialsCitation>
; 
<specimenCount pageId="4" pageNumber="115" type="female">six females</specimenCount>
and 
<specimenCount box="[316,453,420,449]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" type="male">five males</specimenCount>
, Goldash Borujerd, 
<date box="[714,886,420,449]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" value="2018-07-28">28 July 2018</date>
; 
<specimenCount box="[901,1042,420,449]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" type="female">17 females</specimenCount>
