<bibRefCitation author="Hayatolgheyb, S." box="[160,419,641,670]" pageId="4" pageNumber="115" refId="ref3816" refString="Hayatolgheyb, S. (2016) The faunistic study of Eriophyidae family (Acari: Prostigmata) in South regions of Lorestan Province, Iran. M. Sc. thesis of Agricultural Entomology, Lorestan University, 77 pp." type="book" year="2016">Hayatolgheyb 2016</bibRefCitation>
